<%- include('partials/head') %>
<%- include('partials/navbar') %>

<section class="section" style="padding-top: 140px;">
    <div class="section-head">
        <span class="section-eyebrow">Support</span>
        <h1 class="section-title" style="margin: 0 auto 16px; text-align: center;">Frequently asked questions</h1>
        <p class="section-subtitle" style="text-align: center;">Everything you need to know before you start trading. Can't find your answer? Reach out below.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-list" style="max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <details class="faq-item" open>
            <summary>
                <span>What is <%= site.name %>?</span>
                <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
            </summary>
            <p><%= site.name %> is a professional cryptocurrency trading platform that lets you trade Bitcoin and other assets safely, with real-time price tracking and transparent execution.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>
                <span>How do I start trading?</span>
                <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
            </summary>
            <p>Create an account, verify your email, and deposit funds to get started. The platform is built to guide both first-time traders and experienced ones.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>
                <span>Is my money safe?</span>
                <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
            </summary>
            <p>Yes. We use industry-standard security &mdash; encryption, secure authentication, and regular security audits &mdash; to protect your funds and data.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>
                <span>What can I trade?</span>
                <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
            </summary>
            <p>Bitcoin (BTC) is supported today, with Ethereum (ETH), Litecoin (LTC), and other major assets on the roadmap.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>
                <span>How do I contact support?</span>
                <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
            </summary>
            <p>
                Our team is available 24/7 through the contact form on the site, or by email at
                <% if (site.support_email) { %><a href="mailto:<%= site.support_email %>" style="color: var(--signal);"><%= site.support_email %></a><% } else { %>our support address<% } %>.
            </p>
        </details>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-band" style="margin-top: 56px;">
        <h2>Still have questions?</h2>
        <p>Our support team is online around the clock.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">
            <i class="fas fa-headset"></i>
            Contact support
        </a>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .faq-item {
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--edge);
        border-radius: 14px;
        padding: 4px 22px;
        margin-bottom: 14px;
        transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
    }
    .faq-item[open] { border-color: var(--signal); }
    .faq-item summary {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 18px 0;
        font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 16px;
        cursor: pointer;
        list-style: none;
    }
    .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
    .faq-item summary i {
        color: var(--mist);
        font-size: 13px;
        transition: transform 0.25s ease;
        flex-shrink: 0;
        margin-left: 16px;
    }
    .faq-item[open] summary i { transform: rotate(180deg); color: var(--signal); }
    .faq-item p {
        color: var(--mist);
        font-size: 14.5px;
        line-height: 1.75;
        padding-bottom: 20px;
    }
</style>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
